---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About David Kitching - KitchingArt"
  description="David Kitching is a British digital artist based in Cyprus with over 30 years of experience creating original giclee canvas art prints."
>
  <section class="about-page section">
    <div class="container about-content">
      <h1>About me</h1>

      <div class="about-body">
        <p>I'm David Kitching, a British digital artist based in Cyprus. I've been creating digital art for over 30 years.</p>

        <p>My work spans abstract, interpretive, and photographic collections. Each piece is produced as a high-quality giclee canvas print, made on demand to your specification.</p>

        <p>I'm a one man band. Some of my Collections have taken years to finish whilst others were finished in weeks. Most are unrepeatable as they are the result of myriad processes that I could not repeat correctly.</p>

        <p>I want you to be happy with what arrives at your home. Both the quality and also that you like it and that it becomes a welcoming part of your home, promoting wellbeing and good thoughts for many years to come.</p>

        <p>You can always talk directly to me if you have a problem.</p>

        <p class="about-signature">David Kitching</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-content {
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .about-content h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about-body p {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .about-signature {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
</style>
